  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study evaluates the effects of a supervised exercise program on the physical performance,
      the mood and the complications of therapy in patients undergoing a high-dose chemotherapy
      followed by an autologous peripheral blood stem cell transplantation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
