  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18-70

          -  Hematological disease

          -  Treatment with high-dose chemotherapy followed by autologous stem cell transplantation

          -  Understanding of written German

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Cardiorespiratory, metabolical, osteoarticular or immunological diseases which can be
             aggravated by exercise

          -  Pathological stress-ECG at admission
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
